headline: Hubbell (HUBB) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of electrical and electronic products company Hubbell (NYSE:HUBB) jumped 3% in the afternoon session after Bernstein SocGen Group reiterated its "Outperform" rating on the stock.
